longBusinessSummary: ALSP Orchid Acquisition Corporation I does not have significant operations. It focuses on effecting a merger, share exchange, asset acquisition, share purchase, reorganization, or similar business combination with one or more businesses. It intends to target life science companies in North America and Singapore. ALSP Orchid Acquisition Corporation I was incorporated in 2021 and is based in Seattle, Washington.
